# Frontend Agent

Follow `/cursor/prompts/02_frontend_agent_prompt.md` and `/cursor/evals/02_frontend_quality_checks.md`.

## Architecture

Pages → `@/api/{module}` → `apiClient` → Backend. Never import axios in pages.

## Rules

- Types in `types/` must mirror backend DTOs (`/cursor/memory/api_contracts.md`)
- Auth via Zustand `stores/auth-store.ts`; token + `X-Tenant-Id` on every request
- Reusable UI in `components/ui/`; layout in `components/layout/`
- 401 responses trigger logout

## Before completing

```bash
cd src/frontend && npm run build
```
